<div class = "app-card-container">
  <div class = "card">

    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class = "row">
      <div class = "col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag"profile_img.jpg", width: 300, alt: "Proflie Image", class: 'profile-img' %> <!--this is a view helper -->
      
 
      </div>



      <div class = "col-md-8">
        <p>Sometimes I call myself a spoken word poet, other times I just read,recite, 
        perform, watch, listen, compile, edit, promote, suggest,recommend and breathe 
        poems in Nepali, English.I am also an educator and help manage arts and 
